Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.54,0:26:35.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}遠い記憶を辿る
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.71,0:26:41.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}こうじゃなかた事で
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.03,0:26:47.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}輝いてた気がして
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.16,0:26:51.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}眩しかっか
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.95,0:26:54.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あの日を越え
