Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.48,0:27:03.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}始まりとか
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:07.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}どこでもないこの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.24,0:27:09.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}これから僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.47,0:27:11.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}また歩き
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.77,0:27:16.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}新たな夢
